      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just feel like i'm overreacting. it's mostly just fat and puffy, not like i heard a loud snap or anything. i have some ibuprofen here and an ace bandage in my drawer. if i just keep it elevated and iced for like 48 hours, isn't that basically the same thing as what a doctor would do at first anyway? i'd rather just wait and see if it goes down before i spend all that money on a clinic visit.",
